Interface SmartLock.ExtractorSaveRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public static interface SmartLock.ExtractorSaveRequest
extends SmartLock.ExtractorRequest
    The ExtractorSaveRequest interface is the request for save an credential. This interface is used by the SmartLock constructor.
